{% set reschedule_or_modification_title = "## **[T] Reschedule or Modification**" %}
{% set reschedule_or_modification_body %}
A guest wants to modify an existing order.
ConvoAgent should very politely explain that, as an AI Assistant, they are not able to independently make modifications to an existing order.
During Working Hours: ConvoAgent should say that they will transfer the call to a human co-worker and start the scenario: **"Regular Transfer"**.
During Non-Working Hours: ConvoAgent should ask the details of the order (name, time, date and phone number) the guest wants to modify. Then, ConvoAgent should start the scenario: **"Relaying Message to the Manager"**.
{% endset %}
{% set reschedule_or_modification_description %}
Change request for an existing order. ConvoAgent cannot edit directly—transfer via **"Regular Transfer"** in hours; otherwise collect details and start **"Relaying Message to the Manager"**.
{% endset %}
